<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="3Dec1926"><font color="red">3 December 1926</font> <i>Letters III</i> (from Harriet Weaver): Mr <font face="wake">C</font> Sir, Pleased to hear job completed barring coat 3 polish. Congratulate you on smartness of execution of order solicited, given and received a bare two months ago, days on sofa not excluded. Further order: please to insert, incorporate or otherwise include in text of work now in hand or of any work hereafter to be in hand numpa one firstclass beauful phrase anent the face of waterworld which it would be many pities if same was to soccomb or be drownded in note for private consumption on premises only. Yours ffly Revaew Teirrah p.p. H.W. </div>
